<!-- WHAT WE DELIVERED -->
<p class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:24px;">/ What we delivered</p>
<h2 class="h2" style="max-width:664px;margin-bottom:24px;">Everything. From first brief to launch day.</h2>
<p class="body-lg" style="max-width:664px;margin-bottom:24px;">This was an end-to-end engagement, one of those rare projects where we touched every layer of the brand's public presence.</p>
<ul class="cs-deliverables" style="max-width:352px;margin-bottom:24px;">
  <li>Brand Identity &amp; Guidelines</li>
  <li>Content Creation</li>
  <li>Marketing Collateral</li>
  <li>Custom WordPress Build</li>
  <li>Carbon Calculator</li>
  <li>Launch Event</li>
  <li>AV &amp; Photography</li>
  <li>Conference Materials</li>
</ul>
<p class="body-base" style="max-width:664px;margin-bottom:96px;">The website required a bespoke WordPress theme — purpose-built, not templated — alongside a custom carbon offset calculator allowing B2B clients to model their own savings. The launch event brought the brand to market with a fully coordinated keynote, mailing campaign, and AV production.</p>

